         <t:langUsage><t:language ident="en">English</t:language><t:language ident="gez">Gǝʿǝz</t:language></t:langUsage>
         <t:abstract>
            <t:p>Collection of prayers, which were used as <t:term key="Magic" ana="#Magic">magic prayers</t:term>, each of which beginning with 
               <t:foreign xml:lang="gez">ኦእግዚኦ፡ እግዚኦ፡</t:foreign> and often continued with 
               <t:foreign xml:lang="gez">አነኒ፡ ተማኅፀንኩ፡ በዝንቱ፡ ዘዚአከ፡ አስማት፡</t:foreign> or
               <t:foreign xml:lang="gez">አነኒ፡ ተማኅፀንኩ፡ በዝንቱ፡ ስምከ፡</t:foreign> and with <t:foreign xml:lang="gez">ʾasmāt</t:foreign>, 
               some of which are styled according to the Hebrew or Syriac alphabet.</t:p>
         </t:abstract>
         <t:textClass>
            <t:keywords scheme="#ethioauthlist">
               <t:term key="Prayers" ana="#Prayers"/>
               <t:term key="Magic" ana="#Magic"/>
            </t:keywords>
         </t:textClass>
